Output "screenshot.gif"
Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set FontSize 16
Set Padding 8
Set TypingSpeed 20ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Type "clear"
Enter
Type "direktiv"
Enter
Sleep 1200ms

# Light navigation in the TUI
Down
Down
Enter
Sleep 1.5s
Space
Sleep 1.5s
Type "?"
Sleep 1.5s
Type "n"
Sleep 1.5s
Escape
Sleep 1.5s
Type "a"
Sleep 2s
Escape
Type "q"
Sleep 400ms
